Taking typical values: 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{\ce{O2}}(p=2\,\mathrm{Pa})\approx8\,$
\end_inset

mm, 
\begin_inset Formula $T\approx300\,$
\end_inset

K, 
\begin_inset Formula $T_{e}\approx3\cdot10^{4}\,$
\end_inset

K, 
\begin_inset Formula $n_{0}\approx10^{16}\,$
\end_inset


