U_{w\,\mathrm{matrix}}(t)=\frac{en_{0}}{2\epsilon_{0}}\left(\frac{I_{\mathrm{RF}}}{e\,n_{0}A_{w}\omega_{\mathrm{RF}}}\,\left(1-\sin(\omega_{\mathrm{RF}}t)\right)\right)^{2}
